    • 枚举常量概要

      枚举常量 
      枚举常量和说明
      POSTFIX_ERROR_CODE
      Postfix the error code at the end of the generated message code. e.g.: object name + "." + field + "." + errorCode
      PREFIX_ERROR_CODE
      Prefix the error code at the beginning of the generated message code. e.g.: errorCode + "." + object name + "." + field
